div.div: The project has its own token : the ERC-20 compliant SAND token.
The supply (Max Supply) is fixed (3 billion tokens).
The demand of the users will thus make vary the value of the token.
Users can earn tokens by participating in certain activities (sale of digital assets, ...).
There is no specific mechanism for inflation or deflation.
